# Backend Cursor Configuration

This project is a WhatsApp Business SaaS backend system.

## Context

- Multi-company system
- Role-based system:
  - super-admin
  - admin
  - agent
- Customers belong to a company
- System handles messaging, campaigns, chats, templates, workflows

## Tech Stack

- Node.js + TypeScript + Express
- BullMQ (message queues)
- worker_threads (if required)
- PostgreSQL, Redis
- S3 for storage
- WebSockets for real-time chat

